Please remove all smart cards from the computer before proceeding.

After successfully installing this package, this computer can be used to manage and use smart cards for common cryptographic operations such as secure mail and secure web site access..


The following Smart Card related components will be installed:

1. The Smart Card Manager application (ESC), used to manage smart cards.

2. The CoolKey PKCS#11 driver, used to recognize CoolKey smart cards.

3. The CoolKey Smart Card "Tokend" driver, used by Apple Mail and Safari to recognize CoolKey smart cards.

